WEBVTT

00:01:28.310 --> 00:01:31.929
which means I spent the first
30 years or so of my life

00:01:31.953 --> 00:01:34.160
frantically inhaling animals --

00:01:34.184 --> 00:01:36.162
as many as I could get my hands on.

00:01:36.886 --> 00:01:41.466
Why, when I die, should they not
have their turn with me?

00:01:41.490 --> 00:01:43.257
(Laughter)

00:01:43.281 --> 00:01:45.161
Am I not an animal?

00:01:45.185 --> 00:01:49.949
Biologically speaking,
are we not all, in this room, animals?

00:01:51.129 --> 00:01:53.781
Accepting the fact that we are animals

00:01:53.805 --> 00:01:56.936
has some potentially
terrifying consequences.

00:01:57.400 --> 00:02:01.428
It means accepting
that we are doomed to decay and die,